Voting at the ANC’s national conference has been concluded‚ eNCA reported on Monday. About 4 700 delegates cast their votes for the top six from around midnight in Nasrec‚ Johannesburg. Results are expected later on Monday. Here is the final list of candidates for the leadership positions. President Cyril Ramaphosa
Nkosazana Dlamini-Zuma Deputy president David Mabuza
Lindiwe Sisulu National chairperson Gwede Mantashe
Nathi Mthethwa Secretary General Senzo Mchunu
Ace Magashule Deputy Secretary General Jessie Duarte
Zingiswa Losi Treasurer General Paul Mashatile
